Package: rsparrow
Type: Package
Title: SPARROW Water-Quality Modeling
Version: 2.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lillian", "Gorman Sanisaca",
           email = "lgormansanisaca@usgs.gov", role = "aut"),
    person("Kyle", "Hurley",
           email = "khurley@usgs.gov", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Richard", "Alexander",
           email = "ralex@usgs.gov", role = "aut"))
Description: Implements the USGS SPARROW (SPAtially Referenced Regressions On
    Watershed attributes) water-quality model for static (long-term mean annual)
    estimation and prediction. Provides nonlinear least-squares estimation of
    watershed source and delivery parameters, reach-level load and yield
    predictions with bias correction, parametric bootstrap uncertainty, scenario
    analysis, and diagnostic plots.
